      "titleText": "Intelligence Pyramid of Pain",
      "titleColor": "#00ff41",
      "titleSize": 36,
      "subtitleText": "",
      "subtitleColor": "#2a6b3a",
      "bodyText": "Reference: David Bianco's Pyramid of Pain",
      "bodyColor": "#7ab87a",
      "bodySize": 22,
      "bullets": [],
      "tableData": {
        "headers": [],
        "rows": []
      },
      "codeText": "Hash values     → Trivial (attacker changes instantly)\nIP addresses    → Easy  (VPNs, proxies)\nDomain names    → Simple (new domain in minutes)\nNetwork artefacts → Annoying (JA3, URI patterns)\nHost artefacts  → Challenging (registry keys, file paths)\nTools           → Tough (recompile with changes)\nTTPs            → Hard  (fundamental behaviour)",
